            <title>[SPARK-8202] PySpark: infinite loop during external sort </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-8202</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The batch size during external sort will grow up to max 10000, then shrink down to zero, causing infinite loop.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Given the assumption that the items usually have similar size, so we don&apos;t need to adjust the batch size after first spill.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
